            <h1><span> Football Teams
            </span></h1>    
            <p>There are millions of football teams as football is a sport that is played all around the world. There are teams that originate in England, France, Italy, Germany, and Spain.
            </p>
         <h1><span> 
         <li >Arsenal</li>
         </span></h1>
         <p class="solid"> 
           <img src= "https://medias.lequipe.fr/logo-football/71/300?20180726193311" height= "140px" width="145px" alt="" />
           Arsenal Football Club is a professional football club based in Islington, London, England, that plays in the Premier League, the top flight of English football. Arsenal was founded in 1886 and their current manager is Unai Emery. Arsenal have won the third-most elite honours (46) among English football clubs.
         </p> 
<h1><span>
            <li>PSG</li>
             </span></h1>
            <p class="solid"> 
            <img src= "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a7/Paris_Saint-Germain_F.C..svg/1200px-Paris_Saint-Germain_F.C..svg.png" height="140px" width="145px" alt="" />
            Paris Saint-Germain Football Club, commonly known as Paris Saint-Germain, Paris SG, or simply PSG, is a French professional football club based in the city of Paris. Founded in 1970, the club has traditionally worn red-and-blue kits. Their current manager is Thomas Tuchel.
            </p>
            
              
              <h1><span>
                  <li>Juventus</li>
